title: 72. The Power Of Indifference
itunes:title: 72. The Power Of Indifference
description: Nowadays, we cannot watch anything on television or social media without having political views bestowed upon us. Our conditioning makes us crucify people with different perspectives. On today's show, Andy shares a new way of thinking that can drastically enhance your way of life if used properly.
